      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a respectable shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some light surface scratches and a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors; the upholstery is intact, showing only slight softening of the bolsters on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives well, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
