      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014always garage-kept, not a single scratch, and the interior is absolutely spotless. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh car smell! I'm really sad to let it go, but I'm looking for a quick sale to someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
