    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul already completed for peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The chassis is rock-solid, with documented subframe reinforcement ensuring structural integrity under lateral load. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this specimen exhibits zero paint fade and retains its factory-spec suspension geometry. A true driver's car preserved for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
