      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. The exterior retains its deep, showroom luster with a factory-original finish that has been ceramic coated and stored in a climate-controlled environment; you will find zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and every single electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained with a full documented service history, featuring a bone-dry engine bay and a transmission that shifts with surgical precision. The alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. This is not just a used car; it is a museum-quality example for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
